	   <tr><td colspan=2>Not sure why you are discussing HQ bear pelts in this location under the cape but I have a cp or two to offer for informational purposes only<br><br>HQ bear skins are indeed sold for 20-50pp.  Though the reasoning why that persists is baffling to me.  Sure they are used for the 10-slot tailored bags.  But with the availibilty of a 10-slot toolbox vendor purchaseable for slightly over 1.6pp in Iceclad, the ability to sell the 10-slot backpack has again been made impossible to recoup the price paid for the pelt. Since HQ cat pelts fall alot more frequently and can be made into quivers that trivialize higher than tailored backpacks, 20pp is simple unrealistic a price to use as a medium of skill advancement.<br><br>Please do not be surprised as you take your stack of pelts to EC and find no buyers at 20pp.  It is unfortunate that Verant has decided again to supply a 10-slot container that completely kills the backpack market. (Remember the now deluxe sewing kits?)<br>&nbsp;<br>A simple cleric of Rodcet Nif on Tholuxe Paells</td></tr>
